      "seed": 471573561,
      "version": 27,
      "versionNonce": 715479036,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782792998032,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n- we need to handle ingestion of content from thousands of publishers and the efficient delivery of that content to millions of users\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n- we need to handle ingestion of content from thousands of publishers and the efficient delivery of that content to millions of users\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OjZrxYmr53zd7MWr9Gcl8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3749.327434291111,
      "y": 6398.833158030118,
      "width": 1692.178955078125,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1923767364,
      "version": 7,
      "versionNonce": 1046227908,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793067004,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) Users should be able to view an aggregated feed of news articles from thousands of source publishers all over the world\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Users should be able to view an aggregated feed of news articles from thousands of source publishers all over the world\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tcUV0pPRjUmPHwb6Fs1w8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3703.322894872325,
      "y": 6471.721123096156,
      "width": 1575.615234375,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 878396924,
      "version": 235,
      "versionNonce": 1276473340,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793211886,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Data Collection Service: Polls publisher RSS feeds  and APIs every 3-6 hours based on each publishers frequency.\n- Publishers: Thousands of news sources wordwide that provide content via RSS feeds or APIs",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Data Collection Service: Polls publisher RSS feeds  and APIs every 3-6 hours based on each publishers frequency.\n- Publishers: Thousands of news sources wordwide that provide content via RSS feeds or APIs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GeWVOWvi7aDjXQZ-8Mw6s",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3689.4336885688826,
      "y": 6559.98281791798,
      "width": 1526.5872802734375,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1703907836,
      "version": 41,
      "versionNonce": 5434948,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793243854,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q. What is RSS? \nA. RSS is a simple XML format that allows publishers to syndicate their content to other websites and readers",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q. What is RSS? \nA. RSS is a simple XML format that allows publishers to syndicate their content to other websites and readers",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "S2evx_5SHlybqtW6yHYQJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3682.373313052466,
      "y": 6653.712363683701,
      "width": 1661.967041015625,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1782262268,
      "version": 77,
      "versionNonce": 1435837692,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793376710,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q. Why store images in our own Object Storage? \nA. We download and store images in our own object storage to ensure fast, reliable, and consistent delivery. \n   This avoids dependence on publisher servers, which may be slow or unavailable, and lets us optimize image size, format, \n    and quality for a better user experience",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q. Why store images in our own Object Storage? \nA. We download and store images in our own object storage to ensure fast, reliable, and consistent delivery. \n   This avoids dependence on publisher servers, which may be slow or unavailable, and lets us optimize image size, format, \n    and quality for a better user experience",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
