      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2) Users should be able to scroll through the feed \"infinitely\"\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2) Users should be able to scroll through the feed \"infinitely\"\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OyrcHus3yEBgZmNCMQvyF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3709.462392367995,
      "y": 7691.186031427363,
      "width": 837.6593627929688,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1138363516,
      "version": 64,
      "versionNonce": 759342020,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793888555,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Client automatically sends GET request to /feed?region=US&limit=20&page=2\n- Feed Service calculates the offset (page-1 * limit) and fetches the next 20 articles\n- Database query fetches articles with OFFSET and LIMIT clauses\n- Process repeats as user continues scrolling through pages\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Client automatically sends GET request to /feed?region=US&limit=20&page=2\n- Feed Service calculates the offset (page-1 * limit) and fetches the next 20 articles\n- Database query fetches articles with OFFSET and LIMIT clauses\n- Process repeats as user continues scrolling through pages\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZYoJXluEpeRuyJ4mX-yxg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3728.641286083701,
      "y": 7849.433789708255,
      "width": 1366.7388916015625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2m",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 675324356,
      "version": 17,
      "versionNonce": 1407359428,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782793940527,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3) Users can click an article to read the full content\n- News aggregators don't host articles. When a user clicks an article, the browser redirects to the publisher's URL stored in our database. \n- In production, clicks typically go through a tracking endpoint that logs analytics and returns a 302 redirect to the publisher's website.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) Users can click an article to read the full content\n- News aggregators don't host articles. When a user clicks an article, the browser redirects to the publisher's URL stored in our database. \n- In production, clicks typically go through a tracking endpoint that logs analytics and returns a 302 redirect to the publisher's website.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JnJ16_BclJwuM18mBFrks",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3708.025180950922,
      "y": 8047.057827454732,
      "width": 498.9195556640625,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 458173764,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 1543000644,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782794037325,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "import requests\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\nRSS_URL = \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/rss.xml\"\n\n# Fetch RSS feed\nresponse = requests.get(RSS_URL, timeout=10)\nresponse.raise_for_status()\n\n# Parse XML\nroot = ET.fromstring(response.content)\n\n# Extract articles\nchannel = root.find(\"channel\")\n\nfor item in channel.findall(\"item\"):\n    title = item.findtext(\"title\")\n    link = item.findtext(\"link\")\n    pub_date = item.findtext(\"pubDate\")\n\n    print(f\"Title : {title}\")\n    print(f\"Link  : {link}\")\n    print(f\"Date  : {pub_date}\")\n    print(\"-\" * 80)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "import requests\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\nRSS_URL = \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/rss.xml\"\n\n# Fetch RSS feed\nresponse = requests.get(RSS_URL, timeout=10)\nresponse.raise_for_status()\n\n# Parse XML\nroot = ET.fromstring(response.content)\n\n# Extract articles\nchannel = root.find(\"channel\")\n\nfor item in channel.findall(\"item\"):\n    title = item.findtext(\"title\")\n    link = item.findtext(\"link\")\n    pub_date = item.findtext(\"pubDate\")\n\n    print(f\"Title : {title}\")\n    print(f\"Link  : {link}\")\n    print(f\"Date  : {pub_date}\")\n    print(\"-\" * 80)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
